---
title: Mediterranean Bacon & Roasted Eggplant Fusilli with Roasted Eggplant & Feta
description: Add layers of flavour to fusilli with an array of rainbow veggies roasted in Mediterranean-inspired seasonings. Paired
with a rich cherry tomato sauce, bacon and creamy feta, your finished dish will be transformed into a taste sensation.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mediterranean-fusilli-roasted-eggplant-3513887d.jpg
